#: wllegal/templates/legal/documents/summary.html:11
msgid ""
"Your name and e-mail can be used in version control system commits to author "
"the changes you made; they can be stored there indefinitely."
msgstr ""
"El vostre nom i la vostra adreça electrònica es poden utilitzar a les "
"comissions dels sistemes de control de versions per a marcar l’autoria dels "
"canvis que hàgiu fet, i hi poden romandre indefinidament."

#: wllegal/templates/legal/documents/summary.html:12
msgid ""
"Name choice is yours, and the e-mail address used for commits can be masked "
"by Weblate to protect your privacy. You can enable this in your profile."
msgstr ""
