"versió. El Prestador es compromet a complir aquests requisits i vetllar pel "
"bon funcionament del Servei mitjançant les seves pròpies accions."

#: wllegal/templates/legal/documents/tos.html:359
msgid ""
"If the User identifies any issue related to the Service's speed, "
"functionality, or availability, they are obligated to report it to the "
"Provider immediately. The User acknowledges that events beyond the "
