msgstr ""
"Enviar missatges comercials no sol·licitats i altres correus brossa o altres "
"assetjaments il·legals a tercers;"

#: wllegal/templates/legal/documents/tos.html:452
msgid ""
"Publishing or disseminating any content that may infringe the rights of "
"third parties, including attacks on such persons, or any offensive, "
